很好，这一步你已经开始进入“GitHub表达能力”阶段了 👍
README 写得好不好，直接决定别人对你项目的第一印象。

我给你整理一套**可以直接复制用的高频句式模板（中英对照 + 可套用）**，你以后写项目基本不用再想了。

---

# 一、项目介绍（开头必备）

### 通用模板

```markdown
This project is a [type of project] designed to [main purpose].
```

👉 示例：

```markdown
This project is a full-stack web application designed to manage community services and improve digital interaction.
```

---

### 中文理解

* This project is... → 这是一个…
* designed to... → 用于…

---

### 更高级一点（加背景）

```markdown
With the rapid development of [field], this project aims to...
```

👉 示例：

```markdown
With the rapid development of smart cities, this project aims to build an efficient community management platform.
```

---

